a deal with you.

01:06:40.678 --> 01:06:41.874
115, huh?

01:06:41.939 --> 01:06:43.147
Yeah.

01:06:43.647 --> 01:06:45.514
Here you go. Free.

01:06:46.651 --> 01:06:48.398
Read that.
Can you read?

01:06:48.620 --> 01:06:50.485
